headline: Sunshine Health Awards Over $100,000 in Grants to Strengthen Florida Communities
summary: Sunshine Health, a company of Centene Corporation (NYSE: CNC), has awarded $106,000 in "Get to Know Us" grants to 50 nonprofit organizations across Florida that deliver vital programs addressing health-related social needs.

headline: 1 S&P 500 Stock to Consider Right Now and 2 Facing Headwinds
summary: While the S&P 500 (^GSPC) includes industry leaders, not every stock in the index is a winner. Some companies are past their prime, weighed down by poor execution, weak financials, or structural headwinds.
